refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public voidpht\Thread::addFileTask stringfileName mixedglobals
Adds a new file task to a pht\Threads internal task queue.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Adding a new file task to a thread


<?php

use pht\Thread;

$thread = new Thread();

$thread->addFileTask('file.php', 1, 2, 3);

$thread->start();
$thread->join();




file.php:


<?php

[$one, $two, $three] = $_THREAD;

var_dump($one, $two, $three);


    &example.outputs;


int(1)
int(2)
int(3)
